# start Validation Reply Form
_vrf_PLAT342_2T_0m               
;
PROBLEM: Low Bond Precision on  C-C Bonds ...............    0.02219 Ang.  
RESPONSE: The structure is twinned and modulated and organic fragments 
are correlated with each other by pseudo-translation. Part of the organic 
fragments are also disordered and have pronounced thermal libration. 
;
_vrf_PLAT987_2T_0m               
;
PROBLEM: The Flack x is >> 0 -  Do a BASF/TWIN Refinement     Please Check  
RESPONSE: The structure is also twinned by pseudomerohedery and the BASF/TWIN 
refinement involves pseudomerohedric and inversion twinning
;
# end Validation Reply Form

